{"tid":872911,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"冰天雪地浸地熱溫泉 超蓮去冰島晒泳衣相","createTime":"2018-10-23T05:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T07:26:04.000Z","uid":147522,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"091e881a3ca8b7fdabbc9fee10c06d01c01882be","tid":872911,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/130620_e431857ea4a60e33054daf5576222ea1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F130620_e431857ea4a60e33054daf5576222ea1.png&h=1285a7a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n27歲嘅何家千金超蓮，去完巴黎時裝週之後，今次嚟到歐洲人口密度最低嘅國家冰島。話到明係冰島就緊係凍到震啦，十月中嘅冰島雖然未入冬，但係都已經跌到得返5度左右，夜晚更加會跌穿零度，所以呢幾日見到超蓮嘅IG都包到成隻糭咁。<br />\n<br />\n之但係你又點估到，去到冰島超蓮都有泳衣相睇吖？今日超蓮喺IG貼出兩張泳衣相，見佢一身白色低胸連身泳衣浸喺水中，佢仲寫道：「其實三年前就來過冰島，當時沒有去到blue lagoon很遺憾，這次來拍攝第一天就去了，天氣還很好！」似乎就係去咗冰島著名嘅地熱溫泉藍潟湖，冰天雪地浸溫泉真係極度享受。"},{"pid":"b95859c73c88985dd3eb06badd85e87f43bcb0c0","tid":872911,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:07:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e890870ace6fcdd09d703caced41b67bb1bc4198","tid":872911,"uid":184449,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/23/130907_6cb80b91740f8e91681e98dbc37f4b0e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F23%2F130907_6cb80b91740f8e91681e98dbc37f4b0e.gif&h=5a034669&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ef7c1a98bfe982e87bc5144597b8d9d30f0f5d2","tid":872911,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"其實好撚正<br />\n又靚又有身材又係有錢女 成個何家最正<br />\n吳克群屌到佢肯定好有成就感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd134d2a8edbf17c0f02f272d50da5876e762bc","tid":872911,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:1